column5: I'm no longer SnakeBit!! I got my first muskie of the year yesterday while trolling a spot I always kinda figured would produce. She was about 38-40" long and damned pretty!! Safely released to fight again. My boat has finally got some muskie slime on it.
Congrats!!!  hope to see some pics
way to go!!!! you will never forget your first!!
Congrats to you Bigbuck. I don't think it was his first.
wa'lll then, you'll never forget your first of the year! lol
Congrats fella !! I hope to get out there soooonnn !
Awesome...way to go...slime is good yeah!!
